body_html: @d4l3k //tensorflow:libtensorflow.so is a non-mobile target and is not expected to build for Android. libtensorflow_inference.so should contain everything you need for inference on Android (no training is supported at this time). With the exception of the Java API JNI interface all valid Android targets start with the prefix "android_".
